WHEN John LEHMAN HUTTON Inc. Thomas E. Meador wey bi 42 years, dem dey koll am president and chief operating officer for Balcor Co, one Skokie Ill, wey be subsidiary of di New York Investment Bank.

Balcor wey get real estate say di position just newly created.

Mr. Meador don be executive vice president for Balcor before.

In addition to im former real estate investment, asset management, na Oga Meador dey take am do development, and property management.

Di waka wey dem do na for Van Pell, 44 wey bin resign as executive vice president.

